data.description: A Pinnacle Ridge 5-bedroom beauty with a stunning interior. This home has no detail left undone. Every room is bathed in natural light from the abundant windows. Incredible chef's kitchen has premium appliances, expansive quartz counters, a center island, plenty of gorgeous white cabinets, and walk-in pantry. Expansive covered patio off of dining. Upstairs boasts a generous loft, convenient laundry, 3 large bedrooms and the primary suite of your dreams! The custom 5 pc bath is simply splendid. Full basement has a huge rec room, another large bedroom, and a tastefully done home theatre area. 90% high efficiency furnace, AC, high tech cabling, hybrid H2O, roomy garage, extra storage under stairs and downstairs has a huge bonus storage room.
